reviews.review_text:
Whoa horses Sound is runaway too fast, maybe the original taper's machine was dragging.  Was this recorded off the radio?  Nice set list but something to slow it down.
I have looked high and low for my original reel to reel of a Christmas time 1971 show off WNEW FM in NY.  Maybe the NRPS opened?
